Class ValueCriterionDefinition

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.process.model.ValueCriterionDefinition
public class ValueCriterionDefinition extends Object
Defines a value criterion definition based on a target field ID, operator field ID, default operatorvalue, field ID, and default field value.
